<div class='figure-description'>
A great way to remember <br>
your big day
</div>
</div>
<div class='example'>
<img loading="lazy" alt="Pirates figure" class="example-figure-img" src="/assets/pirates-eda3abd8c9f3de7fd0a00bdda479ae05732e166655d6532d52fe0340e7040bf2.png" />
<div class='figure-description'>
Capture your treasured memories <br>
